short.am,ar,de,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,en_US,es,es_4: AliExpress™ tool for Dropshipping and Shopping. Quick View Sales Trends on the List Page.
short.bg: This extension can help you view information and historical data trends of AliExpress™ stores and their products.
short.bn: Curate the best AliExpress™ products for dropshipping and import their product information into your Modalyst account.
short.ca: FREE AliExpress™ product importer to automate dropshipping. Better alternative to Oberlo. Integrates with Shopify, Wix,…
short.cs: Ali Hunter is the #1 dropship spy tool. Analyze competitor sales, find winning products, and skyrocket your dropshipping business.
short.da: Import and sync products from AliExpress™ to your DSers platform account.
short.te: Rovalty is the Number 1 AliExpress Search by Image for Dropshipping Businesses. Right-click on image and search!

long.am,ar,bn,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,en_U:
FindNiche is free AliExpress tool for dropshipping and shopping.  Quickly view sales trends on the list page.  It also shows which Shopify competitors are selling this product.

Main Features:

1.AliExpress Selling Product Research
● Quickly display AliExpress product analysis results: order tracking, wishlists, and price tracking
● Monitor product history information to help you make better decisions
● Show AliExpress shipping times and costs for products with different logistics options
● Display similar products from AliExpress sellers, sortable by time, sales, and price
● See which Shopify competitors are selling dropshipping products
● Right-click on image information to find similar products that are cheaper or sell better

2. Quick view
Expand product order trends on the product list page to make product research simple and efficient.

3. Recommend winning products
Don't know what to sell? Automatically recommend Trending AliExpress dropshipping products on the home page, category page, and every search page.

How to Use Extensions:
You need to log in to the FindNiche website before using it. 
Use it on AliExpress product details, category lists, and store information.
Completely Free & Unlimited Use! For more detailed AliExpress product analysis, please visit FindNiche.

long.zh_CN:
FindNiche 是一个免费的 AliExpress 工具，适用于代发货和购物。它可以快速查看列表页面上的销售趋势，还显示哪些 Shopify 竞争对手在销售该产品。

主要特点：

AliExpress 销售产品研究
● 快速显示 AliExpress 产品分析结果：订单跟踪、愿望清单和价格跟踪
● 监控产品历史信息，帮助您做出更好的决策
● 显示产品不同物流选项的 AliExpress 发货时间和费用
● 显示 AliExpress 卖家的类似产品，可以按时间、销量和价格排序
● 查看哪些 Shopify 竞争对手在销售代发货产品
● 右键单击图片信息，找到更便宜或销量更好的类似产品

快速查看
在产品列表页面展开产品订单趋势，使产品研究变得简单高效。

推荐热销产品
不知道卖什么？在主页、分类页面和每个搜索页面自动推荐 AliExpress 热销代发货产品。

如何使用扩展：
在使用之前，您需要登录 FindNiche 网站。
在 AliExpress 产品详情、分类列表和商店信息中使用。
完全免费且无限制使用！如需更详细的 AliExpress 产品分析，请访问 FindNiche。
